â€¢â€¢ Pre-Select OptionğŸ‘½Â°Â°
Â°Â°Â° When using the "selected attribute" you can pre-select 1 option. This is your default, regardless of each order in which "<option> elements" are defined.
â€¢â€¢Example
<main>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <form>
      <div>
        <label for="AI">What is your favorite AI?</label>
        <select id="AI" name="ğŸ‘¾">
  <option value="Locally Built">Custom</option>
  <option selected value="guardian">Guardian Angel</option>
</select>
      </div>
      <button>Create</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</main>

Â°Â°Â°CSS ValueÂ°Â°
